=== Neurons ===

neuron SimpleTransformerBlock(dim):
  inputs:
    default: [*, dim]
  outputs:
    default: [*, dim]
  graph:
    in -> LayerNorm#0(dim)
    LayerNorm#0(dim) -> Linear#1(dim, dim)
    Linear#1(dim, dim) -> Dropout#2(0.1)
    Dropout#2(0.1) -> out
